gw.i18n

Enum DateTimeFormat

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<DateTimeFormat>
      • gw.i18n.DateTimeFormat
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<DateTimeFormat>

    public enum DateTimeFormat
extends java.lang.Enum<DateTimeFormat>
    Represents a localized format for a date or time value. These values correspond to the settings specified in the DateFormat and TimeFormat elements in localization.xml.

        public static DateTimeFormat getByName(java.lang.String name)
